      <title>工党重获英国政权的五种方式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/five-ways-labour-can-get-back-to-power-in-the-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为期六周的大选活动让英国的民意调查结果非常一致：预计反对党工党将获胜，党魁基尔·斯塔默将成为英国新任首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/five-ways-labour-can-get-back-to-power-in-the-uk</guid>
