    <item>
      <title>加拿大考虑封锁工厂以抵制中国电动汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/canada-to-consider-blocking-factories-in-pushback-on-chinese-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的政府已经公布了将考虑采取的阻止中国制造的电动汽车进入加拿大市场的措施，包括对进口产品征收关税以及阻止中国在加拿大新工厂的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/canada-to-consider-blocking-factories-in-pushback-on-chinese-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 22:53:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
