    <item>
      <title>中国正在为俄罗斯制造和测试致命攻击无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-is-building-and-testing-lethal-attack-drones-for-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情的欧洲官员称，中国和俄罗斯公司正在研发一种类似于伊朗部署在乌克兰的攻击无人机，这一迹象表明北京方面可能正接近提供西方官员警告的那种致命援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-is-building-and-testing-lethal-attack-drones-for-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 20:42:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登寻求平息抗议，将辩论不佳归咎于旅行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-to-meet-democratic-governors-as-he-looks-to-close-ranks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将自己在与唐纳德·特朗普进行灾难性辩论前几周前往法国和意大利的旅行计划归咎于他在台上的糟糕表现，试图解释这一颠覆 2024 年大选并危及他连任前景的时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-to-meet-democratic-governors-as-he-looks-to-close-ranks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:25:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普 2024 年竞选总统期间的法律案件时间表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-trump-trials-court-dates-legal-timeline/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普正在竞选重返白宫，同时面临多项迫在眉睫的刑事和民事审判——这是美国历史上其他候选人从未面临过的挑战。这些法律时间表有助于理解这一切]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-trump-trials-court-dates-legal-timeline/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 10:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
